/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6647619776879324, \"rank\": 0.504072496994258, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"score\": 0.9816729757052419, \"rank\": 0.014996988425288304, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\"}, {\"begin\": 1201, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.9999989631356503, \"rank\": 1.0345393492950854e-06, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To that end, he has been removed from our commentary roster with immediate effect.\\\"\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ballard had been providing commentary alongside Lizzie Simmonds, who immediately branded his comment as \\\"outrageous\\\".\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\":