m commentating any more at the Olympics 2024,\\\" demanded one viewer, appalled by his remarks about Australia's female 4x100m relay team, calling for a public apology due to the comments being \\\"His comments re Aus 4x100 female swim relay team totally disgusting in today's world.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"score\": 0.9816729757052419, \"rank\": 0.014996988425288304, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Weinstein\"}, {\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"score\": 0.9999989631356503, \"rank\": 1.0345393492950854e-06, \"text\": \"Ballard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._G._Ballard\"}, {\"begin\": 1979, \"end\": 1988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999792544555074, \"rank\": 1.643902940021429e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He needs to publicly apologise!!!\\\"\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian women's squad clinched the gold medal with a lead of over a second in their race.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.30962075472407e-30, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}]}, {\"sentence\":